                <![CDATA[
                    
                    <p>追觅去年 12 月推出 Air Power 17 磁吸移动充电宝，主打 15W Qi2 磁吸充电。</p><p>5000mAh 8mm 123g，官方定价 219 元。</p><p>按下方步骤下单，88VIP 凑单后可使用 200-25 元消费券，充电宝实付 151.4 元，评价晒单再返 20 元（详询客服），折合 131.4 元清仓好价。</p><p>下方两款加入购物车，一起付款结算即可：</p><ul class=" list-paddingleft-2"><li><p>点击下方卡片后 → 点击淘宝 App 右上角三个点“<span class="font-color-orangered"><strong>…</strong></span>” → 点击弹出页面右下角<strong><span class="font-color-orangered">淘金币</span> </strong>→ 下单付款；</p></li></ul><dir class=""><a contenteditable="false" href="https://uland.taobao.com/coupon/edetail?traceId=213e04d117794358578481339e0cc2&amp;srItem=1&amp;e=JX4dZP4wT1WlhHvvyUNXZfh8CuWt5YH5OVuOuRD5gLJMmdsrkidbOWBzzpT26idJYffSRUaLRMnyJnvZaKAS9HyolRPgaGxcOgZTnJJVeYtQ0uUXJlu5kBM0Y1duTYB7aczA%2F1QRyMfyMW3eIAWKRa6LeGhgJY%2B%2FxrWOm542iF3mhpDhiQUdsCHDJFv4HWtFROW6jx6bXtds1cCq%2BnZmGkob9ZRYa9bbqpXc9vysLag2hHMFUUWA%2FQpvhuGuJemkhJFPgaJn9UCxv6%2BLvWntiLcZelJt%2BzjyLo5zui4BV4NEbnIHNDR%2Fgwo3tbp4cVxHt3NYtEDNfLOGSa16IWRN7GUFFgz3RBVH&amp;union_lens=lensId:TAPI@1779435857@212cb236_1500_19e4ea46819_70c5@01" target="_blank"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img height="800" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2026/5/a5e13ab8-a49d-4743-aff6-6330dade02cb.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="追觅 Qi2 磁吸支架充电宝 219 → 131 元破冰新低，支持 iPhone 15W+ 手表充电" width="800" /></span><span class="card-info"><span class="card-title"><span class="mall-data">天猫</span><span class="card-name">追觅 磁吸 + 支架充电宝</span></span><span class="card-abstract"> 3C 认证 可上飞机</span><span class="card-controls"><span class="price">淘金币加购物车 1 件</span><span class="card-btn-deep">直达链接</span></span></span></span></a></dir><dir class=""><a contenteditable="false" href="https://uland.taobao.com/coupon/edetail?traceId=213e04d017794363666331355e0ba1&amp;srItem=1&amp;e=%2B1kNUvxPeqOlhHvvyUNXZfh8CuWt5YH5OVuOuRD5gLJMmdsrkidbOWBzzpT26idJhi7PCjxE0BlKOJ6A0HhO2M15Q1wRhyNfeaG%2BFRwFZsAifcGEnVBYHPjW8dJpq8K62mwCY5fS7rVrTdT7cgXf6jgYSYpxmYtMsb%2Bvi71p7YhlXymvoVZzQ3wF4r%2BZB3L66MC4imfMWi2Yw